\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You have almost an hour of training time remaining. Would you like to work on anything else?\u8221\'94 The Guide asked.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Can you provide me with a bunch of items so I can work on my Identify skill?\u8221\'94 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Certainly.\u8221\'94 She waved her hand and more than a dozen items appeared: an assortment of small weapons, jewelry, pieces of armor made of leather or metal, and small bottles of liquid.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 With a smile, Marcus reached out with his telekinesis skill to lift each item, and bring it closer. Then he would use identify on it and return it to its original position. He largely ignored the information the identify skill provided, since he wasn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t going to be permitted to keep the items, it was just a way to practice two more skills he wanted to improve while he had the opportunity. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Then he spent the last few minutes practicing with his mana bolt until he received the System notification that marked the end of training.}
